Yeah, I would giggle my ass off if somebody who condoned animal testing came back as one of these test animals. I would be so fuckin please I would blow a load. Because it would fair. You condone it when it's something else doing the suffering, so yeah, it would be great to see those same people and their opinions if it happened to them.<br>
<br>
<br>
Is that self righteous? I dunno and I don't give a fuck. It sure as hell is no more self righteous than believing your status as a human being makes it right for animals to be tortured for your benefit. That is what is irrational to me. <p><br>
